alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define
Class ComponentState

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define.ComponentState
public class ComponentState
extends java.lang.Object

The State class describes the state of the scheduling system. The states are:

  • NEW
  • INITIALIZED
  • EXECUTING
  • STOPPED
  • ERROR

Version:
1.00 May 2, 2003
